      <hedline>
        <hl1>Defending Napster To the Editor:</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Jack Singal letter on Aug 31 article holds musicians whose copyrighted work is distributed on Napster are not artists; drawing</p>
      </abstract>
